@host = http://localhost:5121

### Register
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rachel@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login (captures token)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rachel@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Create apartment
POST {{host}}/api/apartments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "neighborhood": "פלורנטין",
  "address": "אבן גבירול 50",
  "rooms": 3,
  "sizeSqm": 70,
  "price": 6500,
  "status": "Interested",
  "contactName": "יוסי",
  "contactPhone": "050-1234567",
  "listingUrl": "https://yad2.co.il/item/123",
  "notes": "קומה 2 בלי מעלית"
}

### List all my apartments
GET {{host}}/api/apartments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get one apartment (החליפי את 1 ב-id האמיתי שחזר מה-Create)
GET {{host}}/api/apartments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update status
PATCH {{host}}/api/apartments/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Visited"
}

### Delete
DELETE {{host}}/api/apartments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test without token — צריך להחזיר 401
GET {{host}}/api/apartments


### Create visit
POST {{host}}/api/visits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apartmentId": 1,
  "visitDate": "2026-05-20T18:00:00",
  "rating": 4,
  "notes": "אור טוב, חניה אין, מטבח קטן"
}

### Verify visit appears in apartment detail
GET {{host}}/api/apartments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete visit (החליפי את 1 ב-id שחזר מה-Create)
DELETE {{host}}/api/visits/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard stats
GET {{host}}/api/stats/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}